T1  - Lower levels of ADAMTS13 are associated with cardiovascular disease in young patients.
T3  - [Erratum in: Atherosclerosis. 2014 Nov;237(1):30]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.atherosclerosis.2009.04.013
A1  - Bongers, T N
