T1  - MTAP gene is associated with ischemic stroke in Chinese Hans.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.jns.2009.04.013
A1  - Li, Shu-juan
A1  - Hu, Wen-li
A1  - Liu, Dong-tao
A1  - Sun, Feng-hui
