T1  - Vasculopathic and thrombophilic risk factors for spontaneous preterm birth.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1093/ije/dyp167
A1  - Kramer, Michael S
A1  - Kahn, Susan R
A1  - Rozen, Rima
A1  - Evans, Rhobert
A1  - Platt, Robert W
