T1  - Additive interaction of hyperglycemia and albuminuria on risk of ischemic stroke in type 2 diabetes: Hong Kong Diabetes Registry.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.2337/dc08-1079
A1  - Yang, Xilin
A1  - Ko, Gary T C
A1  - So, Wing Yee
