T1  - Fish, omega-3 polyunsaturated fatty acids, and mortality from cardiovascular diseases in a nationwide community-based cohort of Japanese men and women the JACC (Japan Collaborative Cohort Study for Evaluation of Cancer Risk) Study.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.jacc.2008.06.018
A1  - Yamagishi, Kazumasa
