T1  - Comparison of arterial functional evaluations as a predictor of cardiovascular events in hypertensive patients: the Non-Invasive Atherosclerotic Evaluation in Hypertension (NOAH) study.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1291/hypres.31.1135
A1  - Terai, Minako
A1  - Ohishi, Mitsuru
A1  - Ito, Norihisa
A1  - Takagi, Takashi
