T1  - Mitochondrial haplogroup H1 is protective for ischemic stroke in Portuguese patients.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1186/1471-2350-9-57
A1  - Rosa, Alexandra
A1  - Fonseca, Benedita V
A1  - Krug, Tiago
