T1  - Impact of restricting enrollment in stroke genetics research to adults able to provide informed consent.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1161/STROKEAHA.107.494518
A1  - Chen, Donna T
A1  - Case, L Douglas
A1  - Brott, Thomas G
A1  - Brown, Robert D Jr
