T1  - Risk of vertebrobasilar stroke and chiropractic care: results of a population-based case-control and case-crossover study.
T3  - [Erratum in: Spine (Phila Pa 1976). 2010 Mar 1;35(5):595], 19050593[Comment in: Spine (Phila Pa 1976). 2008 Dec 1;33(25):2838; author reply 2838-9. doi: 10.1097/BRS.0b013e31818f040d.], 19251066[Reprint in: J Manipulative Physiol Ther. 2009 Feb;32(2 Suppl):S201-8. doi: 10.1016/j.jmpt.2008.11.020.], 21192225[Comment in: Spine (Phila Pa 1976). 2011 Jan 1;36(1):92; author reply 92. doi: 10.1097/BRS.0b013e318200478f.]
