T1  - Examining vertebrobasilar artery stroke in two Canadian provinces.
T3  - 19251064[Reprint in: J Manipulative Physiol Ther. 2009 Feb;32(2 Suppl):S194-200. doi: 10.1016/j.jmpt.2008.11.019.]
