T1  - Plasma vitamin C concentrations predict risk of incident stroke over 10 y in 20 649 participants of the European Prospective Investigation into Cancer Norfolk prospective population study.
T3  - 18175730[Comment in: Am J Clin Nutr. 2008 Jan;87(1):5-7. doi: 10.1093/ajcn/87.1.5.]
