T1  - Polymorphism in the human C-reactive protein (CRP) gene, serum concentrations of CRP, and the difference between intracranial and extracranial atherosclerosis.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.cca.2007.11.018
A1  - Liu, Zhi-Zhong
A1  - Lv, Hong
A1  - Gao, Feng
A1  - Liu, Gang
