T1  - [Ten-year morbidity and mortality in a cohort of dyslipidemic patients seen at a hospital endocrinology department].
T2  - Morbidite et mortalite a 10 ans d'une cohorte de patients dyslipidemiques ayant consulte en centre hospitalier.
