T1  - Increased wall:lumen ratio of retinal arterioles in male patients with a history of a cerebrovascular event.
T3  - 17698718[Comment in: Hypertension. 2007 Oct;50(4):603-4. doi: 10.1161/HYPERTENSIONAHA.107.095638.]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1161/HYPERTENSIONAHA.107.090779
A1  - Harazny, Joanna M
A1  - Ritt, Martin
A1  - Baleanu, Delia
A1  - Ott, Christian
