T1  - Long-term progression and outcomes with aging in patients with lone atrial fibrillation: a 30-year follow-up study.
T3  - 17576879[Comment in: Circulation. 2007 Jun 19;115(24):3040-1. doi: 10.1161/CIRCULATIONAHA.107.709287.], 18234932[Comment in: Evid Based Med. 2008 Feb;13(1):24. doi: 10.1136/ebm.13.1.24.]
