T1  - Functional SNP in an Sp1-binding site of AGTRL1 gene is associated with susceptibility to brain infarction.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1093/hmg/ddm005
A1  - Hata, Jun
A1  - Matsuda, Koichi
