T1  - Plasma fibrinogen concentrations and risk of stroke and its subtypes among Japanese men and women.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1161/01.STR.0000242473.13884.8e
A1  - Sato, Shinichi
A1  - Iso, Hiroyasu
A1  - Noda, Hiroyuki
