T1  - Polymorphisms of the inflammatory system and risk of ischemic cerebrovascular events.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1515/CCLM.2006.165
A1  - Lalouschek, Wolfgang
A1  - Schillinger, Martin
A1  - Hsieh, Kety
A1  - Endler, Georg
