T1  - Alcohol use and risk of ischemic stroke among older adults: the cardiovascular health study.
T3  - 16120841[Comment in: Stroke. 2005 Sep;36(9):1835-6.]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1161/01.STR.0000177587.76846.89
A1  - Mukamal, Kenneth J
A1  - Chung, Hyoju
A1  - Jenny, Nancy S
A1  - Kuller, Lewis H
