T1  - Atypical antipsychotic drugs and risk of ischaemic stroke: population based retrospective cohort study.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1136/bmj.38330.470486.8F
A1  - Gill, Sudeep S
A1  - Rochon, Paula A
A1  - Herrmann, Nathan
