T1  - Association of apolipoprotein E 4 polymorphism with cerebral infarction in Chinese Han population.
A1  - Jin, Zhu-qing
A1  - Fan, Yong-sheng
A1  - Ding, Jing
A1  - Chen, Mei
A1  - Fan, Wei
A1  - Zhang, Guang-ji
