T1  - Synergistic effect of apolipoprotein E polymorphisms and cigarette smoking on risk of ischemic stroke in young adults.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1161/01.STR.0000112973.00867.98
A1  - Pezzini, Alessandro
A1  - Grassi, Mario
A1  - Del Zotto, Elisabetta
