T1  - Risk of ischemic stroke among users of the oral contraceptive pill: The Melbourne Risk Factor Study (MERFS) Group.
T3  - 14631089[Comment in: Stroke. 2003 Dec;34(12):e231; author reply e231. doi: 10.1161/01.STR.0000102416.06059.1C.]
