T1  - Effects of cholesterol and inflammation-sensitive plasma proteins on incidence of myocardial infarction and stroke in men.
T3  - 12045159[Comment in: Circulation. 2002 Jun 4;105(22):2583-5. doi: 10.1161/01.cir.0000017822.82512.62.], 12045180[Comment in: Circulation. 2002 Jun 4;105(22):e9111. doi: 10.1161/01.cir.0000025100.18928.95.]
