T1  - Prediction of stroke in the general population in Europe (EUROSTROKE): Is there a role for fibrinogen and electrocardiography?.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1136/jech.56.suppl_1.i30
A1  - Moons, K G M
A1  - Bots, M L
A1  - Salonen, J T
A1  - Elwood, P C
A1  - Freire de Concalves, A
A1  - Nikitin, Y
A1  - Sivenius, J
