T1  - Level of fibrinogen and risk of fatal and non-fatal stroke. EUROSTROKE: a collaborative study among research centres in Europe.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1136/jech.56.suppl_1.i14
A1  - Bots, M L
A1  - Elwood, P C
