T1  - C677T MTHFR mutation and factor V Leiden mutation in patients with TIA/minor stroke: a case-control study.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/s0049-3848(98)00154-6
A1  - Lalouschek, W
A1  - Aull, S
A1  - Serles, W
