T1  - Migraine and risk of ischaemic stroke: a case-control study.
T3  - 8401105[Comment in: BMJ. 1993 Sep 18;307(6906):734. doi: 10.1136/bmj.307.6906.734.]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1136/bmj.307.6899.289
